@startuml P2P 傳輸協議架構

title P2P 傳輸協議設計

skinparam componentStyle rectangle
skinparam backgroundColor #FFFFFF

package "統一 Envelope 格式" {
  class Envelope {
    +v: number
    +ns: string
    +type: string
    +id: string
    +ts: number
    +from: string
    +to?: string
    +replyTo?: string
    +payload: any
    +meta?: object
  }
}

package "官方保留 Namespace" {
  class SystemNamespace {
    +ERROR
    +PING
    +PONG
    +ACK
  }
  
  class ChatNamespace {
    +MSG_SEND
    +MSG_EDIT
    +MSG_DELETE
    +TYPING
  }
  
  class FileNamespace {
    +FILE_META
    +FILE_CHUNK
    +FILE_END
    +FILE_CANCEL
  }
  
  class MediaNamespace {
    +MEDIA_READY
    +MEDIA_TOGGLE
    +MEDIA_END
  }
  
  class SyncNamespace {
    +INDEX
    +REQ
    +RES
    +DONE
  }
}

package "功能自訂 Namespace" {
  class FeatureNamespace {
    +feature.crm
    +feature.custom
    +...
  }
}

package "協議驗證流程" {
  component [P2PProtocolRegistry] as Registry {
    +register(schema, handler)
    +validate(envelope)
    +getHandler(namespace)
  }
  
  component [P2PChannelBus] as ChannelBus {
    +send(envelope)
    +subscribe(namespace, handler)
  }
}

Envelope --> SystemNamespace
Envelope --> ChatNamespace
Envelope --> FileNamespace
Envelope --> MediaNamespace
Envelope --> SyncNamespace
Envelope --> FeatureNamespace

Registry --> Envelope
ChannelBus --> Registry

note right of Envelope
  **所有非檔案二進位資料**
  必須符合此格式
end note

note right of FeatureNamespace
  **格式：feature.<name>**
  必須註冊才能使用
end note

note right of Registry
  **驗證機制**
  1. 基本欄位檢查
  2. Namespace 註冊檢查
  3. Type 合法性檢查
  4. Payload schema 驗證
end note

@enduml



